</div>

<div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapse2">
<div class="panel-body">
<p>If you have any queries related to the corresponding note, then you can post that query in the &ldquo;Comments&rdquo; box which will be notified to the educator. The educator, then, may answer to your query in the same comment box of the note as per his/her convenience. Any posts on that note will be notified to you in your mailbox.</p>
