<div class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse24">Can I post more than one picture of the product I am willing to sell?</a></div>
</div>

<div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapse24">
<div class="panel-body">
<p>No, you cannot. But you can make a collage of various pictures (preferably 3) to showcase your product as much as possible.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-default mix panel-bg CampusMarket all">
<div class="panel-heading">
<div class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse25">What is the purpose of &ldquo;Comments&rdquo; section inside the &ldquo;Ad Details&rdquo; page?</a></div>
</div>

<div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapse25">
<div class="panel-body">
<p>You can ask further queries about the product to the seller in order to get more clarifications. Similarly, a seller can post extra info on the comments section for the buyers to know so that he can sell his product faster.</p>
</div>
</div>
